  speakerName: "Th\u1EE7 Th\u01B0"
  text: "Kh\xF4ng c\u1EA7n mua, c\xF4 \u0111\u1EB7t r\u1ED3i. H\xECnh nh\u01B0 c\u1EADu
    Shipper \u0111ang \u0111\u1EE9ng ng\xE1o ng\u01A1 ngo\xE0i c\u1EEDa k\xEDnh kia
    k\xECa, c\u1EADu ta kh\xF4ng c\xF3 th\u1EBB sinh vi\xEAn n\xEAn kh\xF4ng qu\u1EB9t
    c\u1EEDa v\xE0o \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c. Em ra c\u1EEDa \u0111\xF3n ly n\u01B0\u1EDBc
    v\xE0o \u0111\xE2y gi\xFAp c\xF4 v\u1EDBi!"
